scene.message:
Clerk: Heey~! Why you little{nl}
brat~!!{waitkey}{clearbox}The safe's back there! That's{nl}
not a place for you to go!{nl}
I'll kill you, you hear!!{waitkey}{ret}

Young Man: The place that had{nl}
become wasteland is gone{nl}
clean without a trace.{waitkey}What on earth is happening!?{waitkey}{ret}

Townsperson: I wonder what{nl}
became of the girl who played{nl}
in the flower field?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: The demons are getting{nl}
stronger. If we don't arm up{nl}
properly, we'll be the ones{nl}
done in.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: So even the weapons{nl}
here are products of{nl}
Sonomura's imagination... how{nl}
strange.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: If even real corner{nl}
stores start selling weapons,{nl}
then Japan

Elly: No matter how often I{nl}
come, I can't get used to{nl}
this shop's atmosphere.{waitkey}
